{"tid":1374098,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為何不要獨立調查委員會？","createTime":"2019-07-27T17:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:19:03.000Z","uid":8512,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ae3e073fa6128d17661fd85ae0cd9b2e3a689319","tid":1374098,"uid":8512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:13:40.000Z","msg":"為何不要獨立調查委員會？<br />\n因為當政府應各界要求宣佈成立獨立調查委員會，整個抗爭運動就會瓦解。<br />\n香港人好容易呃，民情是愚昧的，再加上金魚記憶。<br />\n鉛水事件成立獨立調查委員會，調查之後，無一官員要為此負責，鉛水事件就不了了之。<br />\n612警察濫權，721縱容黑社會暴打市民，比起鉛水事件嚴重百倍，香港人你真的相信獨立調查委員會公平公正，會還香港市民一個公道與真相？<br />\n一旦獨立調查委員會成立，這個多月來義士的血就白流了。<br />\n香港人要有共識，不要獨立調查委員會，不談判，不妥協，繼續流水式勇武抗爭，直至林鄭落台，雙普選。<br />\n<br />\n要撤回惡法，要雙普選，要撤控示威者！"},{"pid":"b43529ba10fb02f4df3bc22f57b4a1381848fb45","tid":1374098,"uid":8512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:14:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cee4b86ad0acf238845f0f81cbf545dd2fe009f","tid":1374098,"uid":8512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:14:12.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"3f5b8e9ba317d05fa53f5b9b8d5ca71686c9301f","tid":1374098,"uid":8512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:14:22.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"9181dd31307bbea8e96a0a9b63e26d12450491d4","tid":1374098,"uid":8512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:14:33.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"9d35bb49d3b6e630ae5351881d91eda0a43227e4","tid":1374098,"uid":8512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:14:47.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"8d89f57d7377541a387a4d5cff5132eba78ebdc2","tid":1374098,"uid":8512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:15:02.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"4fc3dc7fdc49efc905b771a0688d8d7710fe67e3","tid":1374098,"uid":262931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:15:27.000Z","msg":"有道理！"},{"pid":"3b2f575c205101a77c25cfbb712385d9a63af027","tid":1374098,"uid":263175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r